OL,3,CHistoric equal pay win for tens of
OL,4,Cthousands of Asda workers
OL,6,FThe judges compared 14 shopfloor roles
OL,7,Fto 17 "comparator" roles carried out
OL,8,Fin warehouses - all of which are
OL,9,Fbetter paid, ITV News Deputy Political
OL,10,FEditor Anushka Asthana explains
OL,12,FTens of thousands of Asda's checkout
OL,13,Fworkers, customer service staff and
OL,14,Fshop floor assistants, most of whom
OL,15,Fare women, could be in line for
OL,16,Fhistoric payouts after the biggest
OL,17,Fever private sector equal pay claim.
