OL,3,CHistoric equal pay win for tens of
OL,4,Cthousands of Asda workers
OL,6,FA court ruling has made clear that
OL,7,Fmany of the roles on Asda's shop
OL,8,Ffloors, carried out mainly by women,
OL,9,Fare of "equal value" to the better-
OL,10,Fpaid ones in the supermarket giant's
OL,11,Fwarehouses, which are predominantly
OL,12,Ffilled by men.
OL,14,FThe judges at the Manchester
OL,15,FEmployment Tribunal compared 14
OL,16,Fshopfloor roles to 17 "comparator"
OL,17,Froles carried out in warehouses - all
OL,18,Fof which are better paid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
