OL,3,CHistoric equal pay win for tens of
OL,4,Cthousands of Asda workers
OL,6,FIt found that in 12 of the roles
OL,7,F"equal value" was established with at
OL,8,Fleast some of the "warehouse
OL,9,Fcolleagues" - and in one case with all
OL,10,Fof them.
OL,12,FHowever, two of the roles did not meet
OL,13,Fthe threshold, and Asda has already
OL,14,Fvowed to take the case to the next
OL,15,Fstage, in which it will argue that
OL,16,Fthere are "material factors" beyond
OL,17,Fsex that explain why they are paying
OL,18,Fthe predominantly male roles a higher
OL,19,Fwage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
