OL,3,CHistoric equal pay win for tens of
OL,4,Cthousands of Asda workers
OL,6,FMore than 60,000 workers joined
OL,7,Ftogether to accuse the company of sex
OL,8,Fdiscrimination after it emerged that
OL,9,Fthe warehouse workers were earning up
OL,10,Fto #3.74 more per hour.
OL,12,FThe GMB Union and Leigh Day solicitors
OL,13,Fargued that it was an equal pay case
OL,14,Fbecause most of the shop floor workers
OL,15,Fwere women, while the vast majority of
OL,16,Fthose in the warehouses were men.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
