OL,3,CHistoric equal pay win for tens of
OL,4,Cthousands of Asda workers
OL,6,FThe employment tribunal's decision to
OL,7,Fdeclare many of the roles of "equal
OL,8,Fvalue" to the warehouse jobs is a
OL,9,Fmajor step forward for the women - who
OL,10,Fcould be in line for #1.2 billion of
OL,11,Fback-pay and an increased annual pay
OL,12,Fbill of #400 million.
OL,14,FAs well as checkout operators and
OL,15,Fthose on the customer service desk,
OL,16,Fthe victory covered a number of shop
OL,17,Ffloor assistants, including in
OL,18,Fchilled, the bakery, produce and home
OL,19,Fand leisure departments.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
