OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe two roles that were not found to
OL,12,Fbe of equal value were a personal
OL,13,Fshopper (who picks and packs for
OL,14,Fcustomers' online orders) and a shop
OL,15,Ffloor assistant working on "edible
OL,16,Fgrocery".
OL,18,FThe union and its lawyers say they are
OL,19,Fconsidering all available options,
OL,20,Fincluding the possibility of an appeal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
