OL,6,FThe result represents a second hurdle
OL,7,Fcleared for the workers who were
OL,8,Fsuccessful in the case.
OL,10,FHowever, the supermarket stressed the
OL,11,Froles that did not win, claiming the
OL,12,Fjudgment had struck out 20% of claims.
