OL,3,CHistoric equal pay win for tens of
OL,4,Cthousands of Asda workers
OL,6,FThey also pointed out that the judges
OL,7,Fhad used the term "mixed picture" with
OL,8,Fthe other roles. That was because in
OL,9,Fsome cases - "equal value" was
OL,10,Fdeclared with some but not all
OL,11,Fwarehouse roles. However, the lawyers
OL,12,Frepresenting the women say
OL,13,Festablishing "equal value" with any of
OL,14,Fthe warehouse roles is enough because
OL,15,Fall of them are better paid.
OL,17,FThat leaves Asda needing to establish
OL,18,Fa "material factor" - such as market
OL,19,Fconditions - that demands higher wages
OL,20,Fin the male-dominated part of its
OL,21,Fworkforce.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
