OL,3,CHistoric equal pay win for tens of
OL,4,Cthousands of Asda workers
OL,6,FAn Asda spokesperson said: "We
OL,7,Fstrongly reject any claim that Asda's
OL,8,Fpay rates are discriminatory.
OL,10,F"Asda will continue to defend these
OL,11,Fclaims at the next stage of the
OL,12,Flitigation because retail and
OL,13,Fdistribution are two different
OL,14,Findustry sectors that have their own
OL,15,Fmarket rates and distinct pay
OL,16,Fstructures."
