OL,3,CHistoric equal pay win for tens of
OL,4,Cthousands of Asda workers
OL,6,FThe result comes after an email leaked
OL,7,Fto ITV News in the summer of 2023
OL,8,Frevealed that an independent expert,
OL,9,Fwho was commissioned by the court to
OL,10,Fcompare the store workers' jobs to
OL,11,Fthose in the distribution centres, had
OL,12,Fconcluded that the women's roles were
OL,13,Fof equal value.
OL,15,FNadine Houghton, GMB National Officer,
OL,16,Fsaid: "This is a historic step towards
OL,17,Fsecuring equal pay justice for tens of
OL,18,Fthousands of Asda workers, but it is
OL,19,Ftainted with bitter disappointment for
OL,20,Fthose who now face an appeal.
