OL,3,CHistoric equal pay win for tens of
OL,4,Cthousands of Asda workers
OL,6,F"These women have been fighting for
OL,7,Fwhat they are owed for more than ten
OL,8,Fyears and are close to ending the era
OL,9,Fof retailers systematically
OL,10,Fundervaluing women.
OL,12,F"It's telling many of the roles judged
OL,13,Fto be of equal value are the
OL,14,Ftraditional shop floor roles women
OL,15,Fhave held in retail for so long."
OL,17,FBut she admitted it was a "crushing
OL,18,Fblow" for those where the roles were
OL,19,Fnot considered to be equal value,
OL,20,Fwhich could cover up to a third of the
OL,21,Fclaimants.
