OL,6,FNevertheless, it is a major victory
OL,7,Ffor tens of thousands of those who
OL,8,Fbrought the case.
OL,10,F"GMB now calls on Asda to stop wasting
OL,11,Ftime and money dragging this case
OL,12,Fthrough the courts and get round the
OL,13,Ftable with us to agree a settlement,"
OL,14,FMs Houghton said.
