OL,3,CHistoric equal pay win for tens of
OL,4,Cthousands of Asda workers
OL,6,FLauren Lougheed, Partner at Leigh Day,
OL,7,Fagreed that it was disappointing for
OL,8,Fsome but a major victory for others:
OL,9,F"Equal pay is a fundamental right, and
OL,10,Fthis decision takes us one step closer
OL,11,Fto ensuring that the hardworking
OL,12,Fcolleagues in Asda's stores are not
OL,13,Fundervalued and are paid what they are
OL,14,Fowed.
OL,16,F"Our clients' demand is clear: they
OL,17,Fwant to be treated fairly. This means
OL,18,Fbeing paid the same as their
OL,19,Fcolleagues in other parts of the
OL,20,Fbusiness, who do work of equal value."
